<br>
And yes, you're right, it's probably the same in other communities that aren't well mixed.<br>
<br>
But why do people feel the need to make such associations?  It just blows my mind.<br>
<br>
Where I'm living now is just completely WHITE!!  It's kind of scary.  You actually start taking a second look when you see a person of color on the streets. &lt;grin&gt; I've never lived in such a place in my life.<br>
<br>
Is all of Washington like this, or just the small towns? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Maritzia Tinkerboltz</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
